bio: Bringing insights to life as a Researcher and Threadooor.
impactDescription:
People are hesitant to familiarize themselves with new ecosystems and don't know how to complete transactions.

With my content, I think people learn how to log in to the ecosystem and what apps they can use in the ecosystem, so I've helped people learn and use optimism.
contributionDescription:
People are generally hesitant to test new things when it comes to blockchain.

The easiest way to instill this in them is to show them that there is an opportunity here, and I've used this in my content to create visuals and video content to make it easier for people to make transactions here.
